{"tid":1958722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列17: 本港次季GDP跌5.2% 港大料失業率達4.5%","createTime":"2020-04-05T01:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T05:49:12.000Z","uid":292292,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7a851c7ec258a65977298938b97f6c08df321833","tid":1958722,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎打擊全球經濟，香港大學香港經濟及商業策略研究所亞太經濟合作研究項目公布，預料香港本地及外部需求於今年首季面臨崩塌式下滑，實質GDP(本地生產總值)預計按年跌8.3%，全球疫情急促擴散拖累發達國家陷入經濟衰退，在疫情、中美貿易磨擦及石油價格戰的陰霾下，預期經濟收縮將持續，第二季實質GDP跌幅收窄至5.2%，但已連跌4個季度，失業率將由首季3.9%惡化至4.5%。今年首兩季通脹率分別為2.1%和1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n面對不利的經濟環境，預期全年經濟將收縮3%，比上次公布的全年預測下調3.4個百分點，將是自1998年亞洲金融風暴以來最大跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%AC%A1%E5%AD%A3gdp%E8%B7%8C5-2-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%99%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E9%81%944-5-214017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%25AD%25A3gdp%25E8%25B7%258C5-2-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%2581%25944-5-214017&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=08db608b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%AC%A1%E5%AD%A3gdp%E8%B7%8C5-2-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%99%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E9%81%944-5-214017</a>"},{"pid":"bb1131c39dbad0ad012ca1873cbdea370d56d77b","tid":1958722,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:10:00.000Z","msg":"港共自己揀攬炒，落實五大訴求就無事"},{"pid":"3dd0e6f868b57a49d294190135899695fcabfcd2","tid":1958722,"uid":83713,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"4.5咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把國家係full employment level"},{"pid":"3a1fd95fd1b1377274c36f87477d8e9865c8fc38","tid":1958722,"uid":67468,"li